		<div class="wrapper" id="Jwrapper">
			<div class="inner">
				<div class="col-a">
					<div class="article artText">
						<h1 class="title">没有前雾灯的车，买了会吃亏吗？</h1>
						<div class="meta">
							<span class="muted update"><i></i><em>2017-03-29</em></span>
							
							<span class="muted view"><i></i><em>6.2万</em></span>
							<a href="http://hj.pcauto.com.cn/article/17776.html#commentPlaceHolder">
								<span class="muted cmt"><em><i></i>22</em></span>
							</a>
						</div>
						<div class="content"><p style="text-align:justify;color:#5D5D5D;font-family:helvetica, Arial, 'Hiragino Sans GB', 'Microsoft YaHei', simsun;">
	<img src="http://img.pconline.com.cn/images/upload/upc/tx/autohm/1703/29/c2/40748734_1490777332695_640x480.jpg" data-meta="http://img.pconline.com.cn/images/upload/upc/tx/autohm/1703/29/c2/40748734_1490777332695_640x480.jpg" class="bigimg"> 
</p>
<p style="text-align:justify;color:#5D5D5D;font-family:helvetica, Arial, 'Hiragino Sans GB', 'Microsoft YaHei', simsun;">
	<span style="font-size:14px;">小伙伴们大家好~</span> 
</p>
<p style="text-align:justify;color:#5D5D5D;font-family:helvetica, Arial, 'Hiragino Sans GB', 'Microsoft YaHei', simsun;">
	<span style="font-size:14px;">今天阿坤来给大家值班！</span> 
</p>
<p style="text-align:justify;color:#5D5D5D;font-family:helvetica, Arial, 'Hiragino Sans GB', 'Microsoft YaHei', simsun;">
	<span style="font-size:14px;color:#0000FF;"><strong>阿坤</strong></span> 
</p>
<p style="text-align:justify;color:#5D5D5D;font-family:helvetica, Arial, 'Hiragino Sans GB', 'Microsoft YaHei', simsun;">
	<img src="http://img.pconline.com.cn/images/upload/upc/tx/autohm/1703/29/c2/40748806_1490777358038_640x480.jpg" data-meta="http://img.pconline.com.cn/images/upload/upc/tx/autohm/1703/29/c2/40748806_1490777358038_640x480.jpg" class="bigimg"> 
</p>
<p style="text-align:justify;color:#5D5D5D;font-family:helvetica, Arial, 'Hiragino Sans GB', 'Microsoft YaHei', simsun;">
	<span style="font-size:14px;">经过了上周<strong><span style="color:#00f;">阴雨模式</span></strong>的洗礼，阿坤觉得自己的小身子骨，再次经受住了考验，看着现在<strong><span style="color:#00f;">晴朗</span></strong>的天总觉得幸福真是来之不易，得<strong><span style="color:#0000FF;">好好珍惜</span></strong>才是！</span> 
</p>
<p style="text-align:justify;color:#5D5D5D;font-family:helvetica, Arial, 'Hiragino Sans GB', 'Microsoft YaHei', simsun;">
	<img src="http://img.pconline.com.cn/images/upload/upc/tx/autohm/1703/29/c2/40748794_1490777358584.gif" class="bigimg"> 
</p>
<p style="text-align:justify;color:#5D5D5D;font-family:helvetica, Arial, 'Hiragino Sans GB', 'Microsoft YaHei', simsun;">
	<span style="font-size:14px;color:#0000FF;"><strong>珍惜美好的时光，从我做起！</strong></span> 
</p>
<p style="text-align:justify;color:#5D5D5D;font-family:helvetica, Arial, 'Hiragino Sans GB', 'Microsoft YaHei', simsun;">
	<span style="font-size:14px;">这么美好的天气，必须得加把劲儿，回答问题呀~好了，咱们现在就开始！</span> 
</p>
<p style="text-align:justify;">
	<span style="font-size:16px;color:#FF0000;"><strong>没前雾灯这车能买吗？</strong></span> 
</p>
<p style="text-align:justify;color:#5D5D5D;font-family:helvetica, Arial, 'Hiragino Sans GB', 'Microsoft YaHei', simsun;">
	<img src="http://img.pconline.com.cn/images/upload/upc/tx/autohm/1703/29/c2/40748833_1490777359110_640x480.jpg" data-meta="http://img.pconline.com.cn/images/upload/upc/tx/autohm/1703/29/c2/40748833_1490777359110_640x480.jpg" class="bigimg"> 
</p>
<p style="text-align:justify;color:#5D5D5D;font-family:helvetica, Arial, 'Hiragino Sans GB', 'Microsoft YaHei', simsun;">
	<span style="font-size:14px;">来，先握个手啊兄弟！关于雾灯，阿坤之前和您差不多，也有过类似的疑问呢~</span> 
</p>
<p style="text-align:justify;color:#5D5D5D;font-family:helvetica, Arial, 'Hiragino Sans GB', 'Microsoft YaHei', simsun;">
	<span style="font-size:14px;">那么咱们首先来说说，雾灯有啥用吧~总的来说，它是用于在雨雾天气行车时的安全警示。</span> 
</p>
<p style="text-align:justify;color:#5D5D5D;font-family:helvetica, Arial, 'Hiragino Sans GB', 'Microsoft YaHei', simsun;">
	<span style="font-size:14px;">在这种天气下行驶，<strong><span style="color:#00f;">前雾灯的主要作用是为对向车标明自己的位置</span></strong>。而<strong><span style="color:#00f;">后雾灯</span></strong>则是“用穿透力较强的光色将视觉信号传递到较远的后方。<strong><strong><span style="color:#00f;"></span></strong><span style="color:#00f;"><strong></strong></span></strong><strong><span style="color:#00f;">”说白了就是让别的车看的见你在哪儿~</span></strong></span> 
</p>
<p style="text-align:justify;color:#5D5D5D;font-family:helvetica, Arial, 'Hiragino Sans GB', 'Microsoft YaHei', simsun;">
	<img src="http://img.pconline.com.cn/images/upload/upc/tx/autohm/1703/29/c2/40748795_1490777360534_640x480.jpg" data-meta="http://img.pconline.com.cn/images/upload/upc/tx/autohm/1703/29/c2/40748795_1490777360534_640x480.jpg" class="bigimg"> 
</p>
<p style="text-align:justify;color:#5D5D5D;font-family:helvetica, Arial, 'Hiragino Sans GB', 'Microsoft YaHei', simsun;">
	<br>
</p>
<p style="text-align:justify;color:#5D5D5D;font-family:helvetica, Arial, 'Hiragino Sans GB', 'Microsoft YaHei', simsun;">
	<span style="font-size:14px;">尤其是这两年雾霾天气出现的太频繁了。雾灯的作用就显得尤为重要了。在<strong><span style="color:#00f;">雾霾</span></strong>里开车，安全是第一！</span> 
</p>
<p style="text-align:justify;color:#5D5D5D;font-family:helvetica, Arial, 'Hiragino Sans GB', 'Microsoft YaHei', simsun;">
	<img src="http://img.pconline.com.cn/images/upload/upc/tx/autohm/1703/29/c2/40748796_1490777360885_640x480.jpg" data-meta="http://img.pconline.com.cn/images/upload/upc/tx/autohm/1703/29/c2/40748796_1490777360885_640x480.jpg" class="bigimg"> 
</p>
<p style="text-align:justify;color:#5D5D5D;font-family:helvetica, Arial, 'Hiragino Sans GB', 'Microsoft YaHei', simsun;">
	<span style="font-size:14px;color:#0000FF;"><strong>提升安全系数的利器~</strong></span> 
</p>
<p style="text-align:justify;color:#5D5D5D;font-family:helvetica, Arial, 'Hiragino Sans GB', 'Microsoft YaHei', simsun;">
	<span style="font-size:14px;">那么有的<strong></strong>小伙伴就问了，我开远光不也行吗？更亮啊~这里阿坤要告诉您，<strong><span style="color:#00f;">远光是绝对不能开的</span></strong>，不仅会<strong><span style="color:#00f;">晃到</span></strong>其他车辆，更会<strong><span style="color:#00f;">影响</span></strong>自己的视线。</span> 
</p>
<p style="text-align:justify;color:#5D5D5D;font-family:helvetica, Arial, 'Hiragino Sans GB', 'Microsoft YaHei', simsun;">
	<span style="font-size:14px;">现在我们再回到“<strong><span style="color:#00f;">好多车没有雾灯</span></strong>”这个问题吧~我知道您说的这个<strong><span style="color:#00f;">雾灯</span></strong>，一定指的是<strong><span style="color:#0000FF;">前雾灯</span></strong>。确实，在大多数低配车型上，都没有配置雾灯。</span> 
</p>
<p style="text-align:justify;color:#5D5D5D;font-family:helvetica, Arial, 'Hiragino Sans GB', 'Microsoft YaHei', simsun;">
	<img src="http://img.pconline.com.cn/images/upload/upc/tx/autohm/1703/29/c2/40748852_1490777360608_640x480.jpg" data-meta="http://img.pconline.com.cn/images/upload/upc/tx/autohm/1703/29/c2/40748852_1490777360608_640x480.jpg" class="bigimg"> 
</p>
<p style="text-align:left;color:#5D5D5D;font-family:helvetica, Arial, 'Hiragino Sans GB', 'Microsoft YaHei', simsun;">
	<span style="font-size:14px;">它们没装前雾灯的原因很简单。第一，前雾灯<strong><span style="color:#00f;">并没有强制性</span></strong>的规定，而后雾灯则国家规定<strong><span style="color:#00f;">必须要安装</span></strong>。所以你会看到有的车没有前雾灯，但一定<strong><span style="color:#00f;">所有车都有后雾灯</span></strong>。</span> 
</p>
<p style="text-align:justify;color:#5D5D5D;font-family:helvetica, Arial, 'Hiragino Sans GB', 'Microsoft YaHei', simsun;">
	<img src="http://img.pconline.com.cn/images/upload/upc/tx/autohm/1703/29/c2/40748853_1490777361899_640x480.jpg" data-meta="http://img.pconline.com.cn/images/upload/upc/tx/autohm/1703/29/c2/40748853_1490777361899_640x480.jpg" class="bigimg"> 
</p>
<p style="text-align:justify;color:#5D5D5D;font-family:helvetica, Arial, 'Hiragino Sans GB', 'Microsoft YaHei', simsun;">
	<span style="font-size:14px;">第二，就是<strong><span style="color:#00f;">成本</span></strong>问题啦！不安装前雾灯能节省很多成本呢，钱的问题，历来都不是小问题~</span> 
</p>
<p style="text-align:justify;color:#5D5D5D;font-family:helvetica, Arial, 'Hiragino Sans GB', 'Microsoft YaHei', simsun;">
	<img src="http://img.pconline.com.cn/images/upload/upc/tx/autohm/1703/29/c2/40748760_1490777363373_640x480.jpg" data-meta="http://img.pconline.com.cn/images/upload/upc/tx/autohm/1703/29/c2/40748760_1490777363373_640x480.jpg" class="bigimg"> 
</p>
<p style="text-align:justify;color:#5D5D5D;font-family:helvetica, Arial, 'Hiragino Sans GB', 'Microsoft YaHei', simsun;">
	<span style="font-size:14px;color:#0000FF;"><strong>大批量的生产，成本控制是个重要问题~</strong></span> 
</p>
<p style="text-align:justify;color:#5D5D5D;font-family:helvetica, Arial, 'Hiragino Sans GB', 'Microsoft YaHei', simsun;">
	<span style="font-size:14px;">现在您应该明白，为何有的车没有前雾灯了吧？虽说这样的车<strong><span style="color:#00f;">能买能开</span></strong>，但阿坤真拿您当兄弟，如果您要买车，<strong><span style="color:#00f;">建议您</span></strong>还是<span style="color:#00f;"><strong>多考虑</strong></span>有前雾灯的车吧~就图个安全啊！</span> 
</p>
<p style="text-align:justify;color:#5D5D5D;font-family:helvetica, Arial, 'Hiragino Sans GB', 'Microsoft YaHei', simsun;">
	<span style="font-size:14px;">现在有的车虽然没有前雾灯，但是有<strong><span style="color:#0000FF;">日间行车灯</span></strong>，它们的作用其实是差不多的~</span> 
</p>
<p style="text-align:justify;color:#5D5D5D;font-family:helvetica, Arial, 'Hiragino Sans GB', 'Microsoft YaHei', simsun;">
	<span style="font-size:14px;">还想多聊两句</span> 
</p>
<p style="text-align:justify;">
	<span style="font-size:16px;color:#FF0000;"><strong>日间行车灯</strong></span> 
</p>
<p style="text-align:justify;color:#5D5D5D;font-family:helvetica, Arial, 'Hiragino Sans GB', 'Microsoft YaHei', simsun;">
	<span style="font-size:14px;">现在很多厂商在介绍自己的车时，都会特意的说：“<strong><span style="color:#00f;">我们有日行灯喔~</span></strong>”那种语气让您听起来会感觉：“哇！好高级！”</span> 
</p>
<p style="text-align:justify;color:#5D5D5D;font-family:helvetica, Arial, 'Hiragino Sans GB', 'Microsoft YaHei', simsun;">
	<img src="http://img.pconline.com.cn/images/upload/upc/tx/autohm/1703/29/c2/40748761_1490777364243_640x480.jpg" data-meta="http://img.pconline.com.cn/images/upload/upc/tx/autohm/1703/29/c2/40748761_1490777364243_640x480.jpg" class="bigimg"> 
</p>
<p style="text-align:justify;color:#5D5D5D;font-family:helvetica, Arial, 'Hiragino Sans GB', 'Microsoft YaHei', simsun;">
	<span style="font-size:14px;">其实在<strong><span style="color:#00f;">欧美国家</span></strong>，日行灯已经<strong><span style="color:#00f;">非常普遍了</span></strong>。不过在我们这里，大家还<strong><span style="color:#00f;">没有完全意识</span></strong>到它的真正作用。</span> 
</p>
<p style="text-align:justify;color:#5D5D5D;font-family:helvetica, Arial, 'Hiragino Sans GB', 'Microsoft YaHei', simsun;">
	<img src="http://img.pconline.com.cn/images/upload/upc/tx/autohm/1703/29/c2/40748854_1490777364938_640x480.jpg" data-meta="http://img.pconline.com.cn/images/upload/upc/tx/autohm/1703/29/c2/40748854_1490777364938_640x480.jpg" class="bigimg"> 
</p>
<p style="text-align:justify;color:#5D5D5D;font-family:helvetica, Arial, 'Hiragino Sans GB', 'Microsoft YaHei', simsun;">
	<span style="font-size:14px;">只是知道有了它是好，显档次，但具体功能可能并不在意...</span> 
</p>
<p style="text-align:justify;color:#5D5D5D;font-family:helvetica, Arial, 'Hiragino Sans GB', 'Microsoft YaHei', simsun;">
	<span style="font-size:14px;">日间行车灯，其实是<strong><span style="color:#00f;">属于信号灯</span></strong>的范畴，而<strong><span style="color:#00f;">不是照明灯</span></strong>。起不到给驾驶员照路的作用，它是让车辆在白天行驶时<strong><span style="color:#00f;">能够让对方辨识</span></strong>，以达到警示作用。提高安全指数。</span> 
</p>
<p style="text-align:justify;color:#5D5D5D;font-family:helvetica, Arial, 'Hiragino Sans GB', 'Microsoft YaHei', simsun;">
	<img src="http://img.pconline.com.cn/images/upload/upc/tx/autohm/1703/29/c2/40748872_1490777366738_640x480.jpg" data-meta="http://img.pconline.com.cn/images/upload/upc/tx/autohm/1703/29/c2/40748872_1490777366738_640x480.jpg" class="bigimg"> 
</p>
<p style="text-align:justify;color:#5D5D5D;font-family:helvetica, Arial, 'Hiragino Sans GB', 'Microsoft YaHei', simsun;">
	<span style="font-size:14px;">它要满足基本的亮度要求，穿透性较强，但也<strong><span style="color:#00f;">不能太亮</span></strong>，以免干扰他人。从功能上来讲，日间行车灯与我们平常看到的<strong><span style="color:#00f;">车尾反光板</span></strong>作用非常类似。</span> 
</p>
<p style="text-align:justify;color:#5D5D5D;font-family:helvetica, Arial, 'Hiragino Sans GB', 'Microsoft YaHei', simsun;">
	<img src="http://img.pconline.com.cn/images/upload/upc/tx/autohm/1703/29/c2/40748834_1490777367375_640x480.jpg" data-meta="http://img.pconline.com.cn/images/upload/upc/tx/autohm/1703/29/c2/40748834_1490777367375_640x480.jpg" class="bigimg"> 
</p>
<p style="text-align:justify;color:#5D5D5D;font-family:helvetica, Arial, 'Hiragino Sans GB', 'Microsoft YaHei', simsun;">
	<span style="font-size:14px;">所以呢，如果您买车时候，<strong><span style="color:#00f;">预算OK</span></strong>的话，还是买一台<span style="color:#00f;"><strong>能有日行灯</strong></span>的车吧。毕竟也是和安全挂钩的。当然，如果实在预算不够，<strong><span style="color:#00f;">没有日行灯也是能开的</span></strong>。</span> 
</p>
<p style="text-align:justify;color:#5D5D5D;font-family:helvetica, Arial, 'Hiragino Sans GB', 'Microsoft YaHei', simsun;">
	<span style="font-size:14px;">因为，<strong><span style="color:#00f;">好的驾驶习惯，比任何安全配置都靠谱。</span></strong></span> 
</p>
<p style="text-align:justify;color:#5D5D5D;font-family:helvetica, Arial, 'Hiragino Sans GB', 'Microsoft YaHei', simsun;">
	<span style="font-size:14px;">好啦~今天的问题阿坤就先回答到这里了啊~欢迎各位小伙伴继续踊跃提问和留言哈！没准儿今天的提问，明天就能上榜呢~</span> 
</p></div>
						<div class="others">
